title: About me
text:
Hi, my name is ti qin, I’m a bioinformatician, currently as a Research Assiantant in Zhejiang University(ZJU) and I study deep learing and bioinformatics!
I have experience with data analysis and graph creation, I love to create new R packages and work as a data visualization freelancer!
I live by the motto, “Humility in acknowledging our limits is the beginning of overcoming biases.”

title: qinti’s Blog
text:
Welcome to my blog!
I’m passionate about bioinformatics analysis and data visualization. Here, I share insights into decoding biological complexities and creating compelling visual stories from data.
Beyond the technical, this blog is a glimpse into my life - from personal adventures to reflections on the world.
Curious to learn more about the face behind the words? Here’s some info about me.
Thanks for dropping by!
